* HTML tags need to be formatted in different ways, depending on whether the
  element is a block, or a span, and whether or not it has to have an ending
  tag.

  e.g.

    (:em "foo")
    => <em>foo</em>

    (:div "foo")
    => <div>
         foo
       </div>

    (:input :type "text" :name "foo")
    => <input type="text" name="foo" />

    (:script :src "foo.js")
    => <script src="foo.js"></script>
